      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Pending有两个出口：支付成功到Confirmed，超时到Cancelled，对吗？那Confirmed之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed",
        "Cancelled"
