      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Confirmed之后仓库开始拣货，进入Processing状态。另外Confirmed状态客户也可以主动取消，要连到Cancelled。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmed",
